ItemDisplay[(rune6_i OR rrorb_i OR pcurrency_i OR psock_i OR pemap_i OR rcurrency_i OR rsock_i OR rcurrency2_i) !zod_i QTY>1]:%NAME%%WHITE% x(%QTY%)%CONTINUE%
